Class DataGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • codetest.DataGenerator

  • public class DataGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    DataGenerator generates test data. It has a single, static method, makeEvents(int, EventIndex), which will add the given number of new events, into the given eventIndex. Created by rgilham on 11/12/2017.
